const selectSongReducer = (selectedSong = DefaultSelectedSong, { type, payload }) => {
    switch (type) {
        case 'PLAY_SONG':
            return songs[payload];
        default:
            return songs[selectedSong];
    }
};

export default selectSongReducer;
